ActNational Capital Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of SASA (SASHA) PALAMAREVIC of Gatineau, Quebec, to be a member of the Board of Directors of the National Capital Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Victor Brunette, whose term has expired.
